⏺ TASK_FAILED

  The model switching failed. I was able to successfully open opencode with
   the Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4 model and access the /models command to
  open the model selection dialog. I could see both "GPT OSS 120B Groq" and
   "GPT OSS 120B OpenRouter" options in the list and attempted to filter
  and select "GPT OSS 120B", but the model switching encountered a
  TypeError: "undefined is not an object (evaluating 'response.headers')".

  The interface still showed "Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4" at the bottom
  after the attempted switch, confirming that the model change was
  unsuccessful. As instructed, since I cannot successfully switch to GPT
  OSS 120B, the task has failed and I did not proceed with the project
  analysis.
